                    and you want terminators to be treated as literals by the parser,
                    then set this to an empty list.

width.description: display width of the aligned text. Defaults to width of the terminal.

tab_width.description:
any tabs in the text will be replaced with this many spaces. if fill_char is a tab, then it will
                  be converted to one space.

truncate.description:
if True, then text will be shortened to fit within the display width. The truncated portion is
                 replaced by a '' character. Defaults to False.
